{"tid":1900274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"點解地盤工人派$1500 可以一個月就搞掂, 派1萬要等到暑假???????!!!!!!!","createTime":"2020-02-27T06:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T09:07:46.000Z","uid":14918,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2368ecf04e36081a5804b7034beea6011e478d","tid":1900274,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:35:05.000Z","msg":"立法會財委會上周五（21日）通過撥款300億元成立防疫抗疫基金，其中基金撥出7.1億元支援建造業，當中接近24萬名現職<span style=\"color: red;\">地盤工每人可獲發1,500元津貼</span>，用以購買個人防護或消毒裝備。<br />\n<br />\n發展局局長黃偉綸今日（23日）在網誌表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">建造業議會將於本星期起邀請合資格的機構和建造業工人遞交申請，申請手續會盡量簡便，以期在接獲申請後2至3個星期內發放補助金</span>。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE HK01唔貼"},{"pid":"817e7409f9b269444c58cf5b78bab7d4374d26fc","tid":1900274,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/2/1582531756_s5-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F2%2F1582531756_s5-1280w.png&h=3309c129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"479a23e0ecf130cda84664d93bea81cb03406126","tid":1900274,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:37:50.000Z","msg":"平時起埋咁多大白象養呢班撚屌 派錢佢地又有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c10053b8551fef6bda0de51ffc04a98fd0ce28","tid":1900274,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4bftTPh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4bftTPh.png&h=bcc12caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.devb.gov.hk/tc/home/my_blog/index_id_378.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.devb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fhome%2Fmy_blog%2Findex_id_378.html&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=4be51a84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.devb.gov.hk/tc/home/my_blog/index_i